modName: NEW mountains rocks boulders and stones
summary: Mountains, boulders and rocks more realistic veined the algae!
descriptionHtml:
Hi all;)

 This modification completely changes the look, mountains, rocks, boulders and stones ...
 In the mountains, boulders and rocks in the slots now see algae!
 In addition, these objects are more diverse color (closer to the real appearance)
 I added texture also suitable for small stones, which often renders the game around the mountains and rocks, have a matching shades of texture in those objects already ...
 Modification compatible with all modifications, landscaping (with the exception of texture modifications which include mountains)
